            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>deae Mi<lb break="no" n="3"/>nerv<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/>Vitalini<lb break="no" n="5"/>us Secun<lb break="no" n="6"/>dinus ful<lb break="no" n="7"/>lo <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>onum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>D in Z. 7 größer ausgeführt als der Rest der Inschrift. Vitalinius Secundus war fullo, also Tuchwalker, inschriftlich in den Nordwestprovinzen kaum belegt, vgl. CIL 12, 01749. 04290; CIL 13, 01906.</p>
            </div>
